  <summary date="2016-02-25T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">CT Colonography Screening for Colorectal Cancer Act of 2016

This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to: (1) provide Medicare coverage for screening computed tomography colonography (CTC) as a colorectal cancer screening test, and (2) exclude screening CTC from a special Medicare payment rule applicable to&#160;certain imaging services.</summary>
